Venezia FC Celebrates The Promotion In Serie A On A Boat Parade

Gianluca Busio, an American Venezia FC player, is celebrating the victory of the Serie B playoff Championship on the team boat through the Grand Canal, in Venice, Italy, on June 3, 2024. (Photo by Giacomo Cosua/NurPhoto)

Personalities Attend The Funeral Of Frederic Mitterrand In Paris

US-born French actress, singer, director, and model Arielle Dombasle is arriving to attend the funeral ceremony of France's former Minister of Culture, writer, and TV host Frederic Mitterrand at the Saint-Thomas-d'Aquin church in Paris, France, on March 26, 2024. Frederic Mitterrand passed away at the age of 76 after a months-long battle with cancer on March 21, 2024. (Photo by Michel Stoupak/NurPhoto)

New York City Columbus Day Parade

An Italian-American man waves a flag of Italy along 5th Avenue during the 79th Columbus Day Parade in New York, New York, on Oct. 9, 2023. (Photo: Gordon Donovan) (Photo by Gordon Donovan/NurPhoto)
